---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { installerScripts } from "../../lib/install";
---

<BaseLayout title="Install ankicli on Windows">
  <p class="eyebrow">Windows install</p>
  <h1>Install ankicli on Windows</h1>
  <pre><code>{`irm ${installerScripts.powershell} | iex`}</code></pre>
  <p>The PowerShell installer downloads the Windows x64 standalone ZIP, verifies its checksum, and installs <code>ankicli.exe</code> into <code>%LOCALAPPDATA%\Programs\ankicli</code>.</p>
  <pre><code>ankicli --version
ankicli --json doctor backend</code></pre>
</BaseLayout>
